<br>
WIS - High as you can get while maintaining resists.<br>
HP - Same as WIS<br>
AC - High as you can get if tanking (you'll only have maybe 3 tanks, if you're not one of them you wont be tanking), otherwise don't worry too much about it.<br>
<br>
Don'ts - <br>
Stun.  Everything in ToV is 60+ and so stuns will not stun (they will land though).  Only use stuns if you are looking to knockback a mob (don't like this myself, seive), or taunt it.<br>
<br>
Look around - be where you're supposed to be.  Or you will wipe out.<br>
<br>
Die to enrage - turn off attack or be behind the mob.<br>
<br>
Overaggro - if you're not a tank, practice your aggro management.  Everything in ToV does solid melee damage, don't make your Clerics lives any harder.<br>
<br>
Push the mob where it shouldn't be.  Be aware of where your melee is directing the mob.  Know where you want the mob to be positioned.<br>
<br>
Get mobs stuck on firepots, flags, etc.  They will warp, summon you, kill you in a bad place.<br>
<br>
<br>
Do's - Heal.  AoE heals are very helpful in ToV to mitigate the many AoE damage attacks.  Other heals also useful.  First trips especially if people aren't quite up to speed on levels or resists, people will take a ton of damage so all healing helps.<br>
<br>
Have fun <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushehabaldean.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shehab al dean</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arabian Crusader</span><br>  Posts: 505<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/14/02 8:27:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=42.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://forzaq8.net/everquest/personal.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ToV tips please </span><hr size=1> lose all the stuns / buffs ( AC / HP ) spell u got<br>
